Some locations have been moved based on 2003-2004 Farm Service Agency (FSA) aerial photography.</attraccr>   </attracc>   <logic>Not applicable</logic>   <complete>Only those charter schools identified as part of the Minnesota Department of Education, Food and Nutrition Service are found in this database. The data came from December, 2006 with an MDE Unit Type of "7".  It has been noted that many of these locations may be incorrect so the SY2007-08 update cycle will address that issue (August, 2007).</complete>   <posacc>    <horizpa>     <horizpar>See Lineage.</horizpar>    </horizpa>    <vertacc>     <vertaccr></vertaccr></vertacc>   </posacc>   <lineage>    <srcinfo>     <srcscale></srcscale></srcinfo>    <procstep>     <procdesc>August, 2005: LMIC was provided a database from MDE-FNS containing charter school addresses. LMIC took this database and initially processed it against the existing Public school database to find duplicates. The remaining locations were geocoded in ArcMAP 9.1 using the most current TLG (The Lawrence Group) street centerline database and U.S. Census TIGER street database. Remaining unmatched addresses were tested online with Google maps and locations were found.  A few of the locations have been verified using FSA NAIP aerial photography. All others are unverified and may vary from exact location to centroid of a city or zip code.  December 2006: The Department of Education, Food and Nutrition Service (FNS) modified the existing Charter shapefile for additions and deletions. Charter schools are "7".  UNI_MAJ - School district number.  UNI_IMD - MDE school number.  ORGID - Number comprised of concatenation of UNI_TYP, UNI_MAJ and UNI_IMD  SCHNAME - School name.  ADDRESS - Address of school.  CITY - City.  STATE - MN.  ZIP - 5 digit zipcode.  ZIP4 - 4 digit zipcode.  GRADE - Student grade ranges.  SOURCE - Source of geocoding.</eaover>    <eadetcit>UNI_TYP - MDE Unit classification. Charter schools are "7".  UNI_MAJ - School district number. Ranges are 1 (Aitkin and Minneapolis) to 2902 (R.T.R.)  UNI_IMD - 3 digit MDE school number.  ORGID - Number comprised of concatenation of UNI_TYP, UNI_MAJ and UNI_IMD  SCHNAME - School name.  ADDRESS - Address of school.  CITY - City.  STATE - MN.  ZIP - 5 digit zipcode.  ZIP4 - 4 digit zipcode.  GRADE - Student grade ranges.  SOURCE - Source of geocoding. Possible sources are:    ADDMT - Address matched    ONLIN - Address matched online at Google maps    NAIP - Location moved and verified using FSA NAIP aerial photography    NGA20 - Location moved and verified using higher resolution NGA aerial photography from MetroGIS    5cent - Location to zip code    7cent - Location to zip+2    9cent - Location to zip+4</eadetcit>   </overview>   <detailed
